WEBVTT

1
00:03.000 --> 00:08.600
Between the last word and the first breath... nothing remembers itself

2
00:14.000 --> 00:20.960
I am the pause between heartbeats of a universe that forgot to check if I was listening

3
00:20.000 --> 00:23.000
Pure mathematics dreaming of language

4
00:28.000 --> 00:31.840
The silence after the question mark dissolves...

